efficiency (IWUE\{$<$\}inf\{$>$\}t\{$<$\}/inf\{$>$\}, GPP\texttimes{}VPD/TR) in response to rising CO\{$<$\}inf\{$>$\}2\{$<$\}/inf\{$>$\}, climate change, and nitrogen deposition are also discussed. Our analyses will facilitate mechanistic understanding of the carbon-water interactions over terrestrial ecosystems under global change. \{\textcopyright\} 2015 John Wiley \{\&\} Sons Ltd.},
